{"tid":2318261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[正式開始]真正屬於香港人嘅香港人FC正式成立！","createTime":"2020-12-09T08:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T12:23:08.000Z","uid":362156,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f2671bd45edc0e43eee5943785d8db2fa2936955","tid":2318261,"uid":362156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CJ4C8ZS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCJ4C8ZS.png&h=8d5d16f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ULWmRdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FULWmRdd.jpg&h=ea4d7958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人，我地究竟經歷過幾多次假希望？最終變成一次又一次嘅失望？</span></span><br />\n2009年<span class=\"red\">南華打入亞協四強，港隊贏得東亞運足球冠軍</span><br />\n2014年香港<span class=\"red\">足球制度改革</span><br />\n2018年<span class=\"red\">港中大戰</span><br />\n再到<span class=\"red\">足總推出鳳凰計劃</span><br />\n加上香港足球一直存在嘅假波問題<br />\n<br />\n香港人實在經歷過太多次嘅失望<br />\n但各位真．香港人，請你比一次機會我地，睇哂以下嘅文字，比機會我地改變香港足球。<br />\n<span class=\"red\"></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">香港足球究竟存在咩問題？</span></span><br />\n－老世足球文化，比錢搞波為威，根本對香港足球發展冇責任心，令到足球隊經常出現搞一兩年又唔搞嘅局面<br />\n－訓練時間與設施水平不足<br />\n－職業球員人工低，引至假波問題<br />\n－足總宣傳不足，令到港足難以吸引人入場<br />\n－比賽欠缺地區性（香港地方細，沒有打比）<br />\n－足球隊沒有長遠目標，欠缺有規模的宣傳（主要都係班費問題）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">咁究竟咩係香港人FC?你地究竟想搞咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人FC係由一班熱血，愛香港嘅年輕人於2020年12月1日創立，請來了<span class=\"red\">前傑志青年軍教練溫遠雄做主教練</span>，我地嘅理念係：<br />\n－必須做好所以宣傳工作（我地有幾位成員有豐富且成功嘅營運youtube channel嘅經驗）<br />\n－以足球為本，教導球員做人處世態度，教大家在場內場外分清是非黑白<br />\n－從地區出發，做好地區工作，借區議會由民主派控制之利，加強球會與地區之關係<br />\n－自給自足，初期由球員以及youtube channel紅利去支持球會開支，後期靠紀念品／球衣，youtube分紅等去支持球會開支<br />\n－目標是取西方經營球會之道，成為香港足球之榜樣，成為香港人值得自豪的球會<br />\n<br />\n我地目前做左咩工作？<br />\n－不斷與同路人聯絡，<span class=\"red\">暫時成功與本地足球用品生產商 Hanstti Soccer達成合作協議，對方願意贊助本球會之球衣<br />\n－<span class=\"x-large\">香港人FC將與Hanstti Soccer公開發售本會球衣，扣除成本後將會全數捐到「6．12人道基金」為香港人出一分力</span></span><br />\n－即將全力營運Youtube channel，盡快有紅利<br />\n－即將開始選拔工作<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">現在，香港人FC請大家幫幫手，做以下工作：</span></strong></span><br />\n－like share 訂閱我地嘅facebook youtube ig<br />\nfacebook： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BAFC-The-Hong-Kongers-Football-Club-105819681386807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BAFC-The-Hong-Kongers-Football-Club-105819681386807&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=6148dfaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BAFC-The-Hong-Kongers-Football-Club-105819681386807</a><br />\nyoutube：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCorYEOWJqiWsTVE_RwSZR1A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCorYEOWJqiWsTVE_RwSZR1A&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=fb4b7f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCorYEOWJqiWsTVE_RwSZR1A</a><br />\nig：hkgersfc<br />\n<br />\n－公開傳播我地嘅理念<br />\n－可以幫手搵贊助（所有贊助商之品牌，將會印係練習波衫，而出價最高者，將會印係主客場哥球衣次胸口位置）<br />\n－多多關心本地足球，不論係踢波定睇波！<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家支持香港人FC!"},{"pid":"5c99972492fde3cee8267eed19f22f7904d6d3ca","tid":2318261,"uid":167512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bebdf74163de4f12cf689b0bf44cd341d3fdc133","tid":2318261,"uid":328267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:15:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"63425063bcf8f5b6bd6845b36df034630f906020","tid":2318261,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"要去波台開多個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd229f94f100dac3e74e5b873d3d16c9469beb6","tid":2318261,"uid":216603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited